data.description: Welcome Home to this move-in ready home located conveniently to shopping, schools, etc. in Arab.  This 3 bedroom 2 bath home with laundry/mud room has been totally renovated within the past two years to include HVAC, roof, water heater, appliances, sheetrock, siding, etc.  Approximately 0.96 acre allows for room for expansion.  Family Room opens to eat-in Kitchen with granite countertops.  LVP flooring throughout.    Call your favorite Realtor today to see this great home before it is sold!!
